metadata.name: WE ALL DEAD #1
metadata.description:
hi im chrysi.

in 2019, i was thrown into the darkest period of my life.

ironically, in all that darkness was where i truly found myself.

music was the only thing i had left in me, so i wrote and produced my first album WE ALL DEAD, inspired by this journey.

TRACKS

1: cold as ice

2: 半影

3: WE ALL DEAD

4: ain't got love for you

5: till july
